<P><HI>LONDON:</HI> Printed for <HI>W. Mears</HI> at the <HI>Lamb,</HI> and <HI>J. Brown</HI> at the <HI>Black Swan,</HI> both without <HI>Temple-Bar.</HI> MDCCXV. [Price 6<HI>d.</HI>]</P>
